LoRAForge/
├─ README.md                # Project overview & usage
├─ LICENSE                  # MIT
├─ requirements.txt         # Python deps
├─ pyproject.toml           # Optional modern packaging
├─ Makefile                 # Common commands (train, eval, test)
├─ configs/                 # YAML configs for models & tasks
│  ├─ sft_default.yaml
│  └─ lora_mistral.yaml
├─ data/
│  ├─ raw/                  # Original datasets
│  ├─ processed/            # Preprocessed parquet/arrow
│  └─ samples/              # Tiny test data for CI
├─ src/
│  ├─ data/                 # Dataset loaders & formatters
│  ├─ models/               # Base model + LoRA setup
│  ├─ training/             # Training loop & trainer
│  ├─ eval/                 # Evaluation scripts & metrics
│  ├─ utils/                # Logging, I/O, helpers
│  └─ cli/                  # Command-line entrypoints
├─ scripts/                 # One-off utilities (prepare_data, export, push_to_hub)
├─ tests/                   # Unit tests for CI
└─ .github/workflows/ci.yaml # GitHub Actions CI
